data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home nestled in Tradewinds. The open living area and kitchen create a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining family and friends. The spacious bedrooms offer ample natural light and closet space, providing a comfortable room. Enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities and the peaceful ambiance of this wonderful community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!
